1.下载Python运行环境https://www.python.org/
  设置环境变量
2.下载集成开发环境（IDE）https://www.jetbrains.com/
3.配置pycharm，
  a.设置行号file->settings->editor->general->appearance
  b.设置字体file->settings->editor->colors&fonts->font
  c.设置整体背景file->settings->appearance&behavior
4.安装requests
  a.http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/
  b.搜索requests，将下载后的whl后缀改为zip，解压后将requests文件夹复制到Python中lib文件夹
